title: Clinton ‘Out of Touch’ With Whistleblowers Reality - Ex Snowden Attorney
text: Presidential candidate Hillary Clinton showed a lack of understanding of the difficulties US whistleblower evidenced by her remarks during the debate of Democratic presidential hopefuls on Tuesday, former Edward Snowden attorney Jesslyn Radack said. ...
